Tha Connect is the debut studio album by American rapper Willy Northpole. It was 
released on June 23, 2009. The album's first single was "Body Marked Up" and second 
"#1 Side Chick" Ft. Bobby Valentino. The album features guest appearances from Ne-Yo,
B.o.B, and Bobby Valentino. The albums first week sales were 2,896. As of October 18, 2009 
the album has 7,000 record sales...
